Name: cs_speak
Author: Swampy
Category: ChanServ
Last updated: 2011-01-03T02:24:53+00:00

Allows users to talk via ChanServ but they must have access rights on CA_SAY in order to use the function (so you can set SAY rights to any level you wish.

Provides commands:
/ChanServ Speak [#Channel] [Text Here]

Also writes to log to say whos used the command, what they said via ChanServ and what channel it was said on. (ideal for anyone who abuses it)

Version 1.0 supports Anope 1.8.5 to 1.8.6
